Stana Katic https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stana_Katic 0 Stana Katic (; born 26 April 1978) is a Canadian-American film and television actress. She played Kate Beckett on the ABC television romantic crime series Castle (2009–2016) and Agent Emily Byrne in the thriller series Absentia (2017–).
